{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "73710ca0-5186-4d83-ad51-a12af360f61d", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/73710ca0-5186-4d83-ad51-a12af360f61d@3.pkg/1772597541060/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597541364", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/73710ca0-5186-4d83-ad51-a12af360f61d@3.pkg/1772597541060/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597541364"}, "identifier": "73710ca0-5186-4d83-ad51-a12af360f61d", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①④：结合所学知识可知，题文图片反映了宪法是国家的根本法，宪法具有最高的法律地位；宪法是其他法律的立法基础和立法依据，故①④解读正确；</p>\n\n<p>②国家生活中的具体化问题是由普通法律规定的，宪法规定的是国家生活中的根本问题，故②解读错误；</p>\n\n<p>③：观点本身正确，但不能从图片体现出来，故③解读错误。</p>\n\n<p>本题是逆向选择题，故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2023湖北十堰中考真题）宪法是国家的根本法。对下边图示解读不恰当的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\"><img src=\"${ref-path}/edu/questions/image.png\">​</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">①在法律体系中宪法具有最高的法律地位&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">②国家生活中的具体化问题是由宪法规定</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">③宪法是一切组织和个人的根本活动准则</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">④宪法是其他法律的立法基础和立法依据</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2023湖北十堰中考真题）宪法是国家的根本法。对下边图示解读不恰当的是（    ）①在法律体系中宪法具有最高的法律地位    ②国家生活中的具体化问题是由宪法规定③宪法是一切组织和个人的根本活动准则④宪法是其他法律的立法基础和立法依据", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/73710ca0-5186-4d83-ad51-a12af360f61d@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754822496017", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2023湖北十堰中考真题）宪法是国家的根本法。对下边图示解读不恰当的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\"><img src=\"https://bdcs-file-2.ykt.cbern.com.cn/esp_courseareobject/k12-exercises/default/attachments/e0a4c0ce-1d5c-8da0-a5f5-4c7d8385eea8.png\" style=\"\" />​</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">①在法律体系中宪法具有最高的法律地位&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">②国家生活中的具体化问题是由宪法规定</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">③宪法是一切组织和个人的根本活动准则</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">④宪法是其他法律的立法基础和立法依据</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec6